      "description": "Pump hydraulic performance (pressure head vs. flow rate) validated against manufacturer test data and FDA benchmark experimental measurements. CFD predictions within 5% of measured values across the full operating range. Turbulence model sensitivity study confirms k-omega SST selection is appropriate for this geometry.",
