      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver holds ISO 9001 certification and has documented V&V test suite with version-controlled releases.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 is deployed under an ISO 9001-certified quality management system. Release notes, regression test suite results, and change logs are archived in the sponsor's document control system. All simulation runs executed from a locked solver version with audit trail."
