      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes benchmark verification cases relevant to rotating machinery and viscous internal flows.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent verified against ASME V&V 20 benchmark cases for lid-driven cavity, backward-facing step, and rotating annulus flows. Observed order of convergence matches theoretical second-order accuracy. No anomalous behavior detected in relevant flow regimes."
