      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% for primary QoIs on final production mesh.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted on 1.2M, 4.8M, and 19.2M cell meshes. Richardson extrapolation yields GCI of 1.8% for NIH and 2.1% for pressure head on the 4.8M cell production mesh. Observed order of convergence p=1.94, consistent with second-order spatial discretization. Production mesh selected as mesh-independent for all five operating conditions."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
