      "rationale": "At Model Risk Level 2 with Medium model influence, numerical solver error beyond code verification is not required per ASME V&V 40 Table 3. Solver residuals converged to 1e-6 for all equations in all runs, providing sufficient confidence without formal iterative error quantification."
