      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on published literature demonstrating superior performance for rotating blood pump flows. Model form uncertainty not formally quantified at MRL 2, but turbulence model sensitivity study (k-epsilon comparison) showed less than 3% difference in NIH predictions, providing qualitative confidence in model form selection."
    },
